When submitting defect reports to Upspring Software, please include
the following information:

Your name and contact information.
Company name.
Date.
Product and version.
Operating System.
Description of the problem.
  [ Please give details on how to reproduce the problem. ]
Relevant log files.
Your goal.
  [ Please provide exact description of what you planned to achieve when the
    defect was encountered]


Defect reports may be emailed to support@upspringsoftware.com, or sent via
fax to 781-359-3399.
